        <mxCell id="ragSteps" value="Runtime RAG Steps&#xa;1. Check if turn is follow-up&#xa;2. Rewrite follow-up to standalone question&#xa;3. Create original + 3 similar questions&#xa;4. BM25 + vector retrieval per question&#xa;5. Merge duplicate chunks&#xa;6. Rerank to 6 chunks&#xa;7. Generate answer + citations&#xa;8. Generate follow-ups and diagram decision" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#faf5ff;strokeColor=#a855f7;fontSize=12;align=left;spacing=8;" vertex="1" parent="engineGroup">
